{"word":"G664 - ἀποτόμως - apotómōs - ap-ot-om'-oce - Sharply","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἀποτόμως</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">apotómōs</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ap-ot-om'-oce</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Sharply</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adverb / வினையடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"கண்டிதம் பண்ணு, கண்டிப்பாய் - வினையடை"},{"paragraph":"abruptly, precipitously, sharply, severely"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Adverb from a derivative of a compound of <a href=\"#/G575 - ἀπό - apó - apo'/575\">G575</a> and <b>&#x03C4;&#x03B5;&#x0301;&#x03BC;&#x03BD;&#x03C9;</b> <b>temno&#x0304;</b> (to <i>cut</i>); <i>abruptly</i>, that is, <i>peremptorily:</i> - sharply (-ness).</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G2699/2699\">G2699</a>, <a href=\"#/G3718/3718\">G3718</a>, <a href=\"#/G663/663\">G663</a>, <a href=\"#/G664/664\">G664</a>"}]}